The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | Death wish
                                                                                                               Death wish
                            
	Bolpur, Aug. 6: A 13-year-old boy from Birbhum, bed-ridden for a month after an accident, has written to the subdivisional officer of Suri seeking permission to die.         
	Mohammed Aslam, a Class V dropout, used to work in a garage with his father.        
	He injured his spinal cord when a part of a car fell on him while he was repairing it in the garage.                                                                                                                                                                              
